==Advanced Settings window: Competitors section==
The Competitors section allows you to set various options related to the [[Main/en/AI:Main Page|AI]] and [[Main/en/Multiplayer|multiplayer]]. The purpose of the available settings is explained below. For each setting, the respective variable from the [[Main/en/Openttd.cfg|config file]] is listed as well, together with its possible values.
